			<dataSelectionAndCombinationPrinciples xml:lang="en">For the large-scale production scenario, annual statistical and monitoring data from Shenfeng Cement Co., Ltd. in Shandong Province, China, were used. Due to the lack of information on the former, direct atmospheric emission data come from Yunnan Hongda Cement Plant.</dataSelectionAndCombinationPrinciples>
			<dataSelectionAndCombinationPrinciples xml:lang="zh">对于大规模生产情景，使用了来自中国山东省申丰水泥有限公司的年度统计和监测数据。由于前者缺乏信息，因此直接大气排放数据来源于云南宏达水泥厂。</dataSelectionAndCombinationPrinciples>
